data.description: Welcome to your dream colonial home in Windsor, Connecticut! Nestled on a peaceful cul-de-sac, this charming residence boasts modern comforts and ample space for every lifestyle.  Step inside to discover a bright and inviting interior, featuring 3 bedrooms and 2.5 bathrooms. The primary en suite offers convenience and privacy with its own full bathroom, while the updated kitchen beckons with sleek granite countertops and stainless steel appliances, perfect for culinary adventures and casual dining.  Entertainment awaits in the spacious backyard, complete with a sparkling above-ground pool and a sprawling deck, ideal for summer gatherings and relaxation under the sun. With a fully finished basement, there's plenty of room for recreation and storage.  Plus, enjoy the benefits of energy efficiency with solar panels, ensuring both sustainability and savings for years to come.  Don't miss your chance to make this Windsor gem your home sweet home! Schedule your opportunity to see this home today and start living your best life in this wonderful community.
